Navigation Instructions

This page will show you how to navigate through this e-learning course.  You’ll also find specific navigation instructions throughout the module.  

Click the left arrow to go to the previous page of this course.

Click the “Home” icon to return to the home screen of this module.

The “Page” icon indicates the page you are presently on.  Click the icon to reveal a drop-down list of all pages in this course.

Click the “Close” icon to quit the course.

Once you have completed all of the interactions on the screen, the right arrow will appear, allowing you to move forward in the course.  Click the right arrow to proceed to the next page of this course.
